%F A274105 From _Eder G. Santos_, Dec 01 2024: (Start)
%F A274105 T(n,k) = Sum_{j=0..k} binomial(ceiling(n/2),j) * Stirling2(n-j,n-k).
%F A274105 T(n,k) = T(n-1,k) + (n-k+A000035(n)) * T(n-1,k-1), T(n,0) = 1, T(0,k) = delta(k,0). (End)
